    "title": "Walk-in Drive Logistics Manager at TransIndia Logistics",
    "description": "Join the TransIndia Logistics family as a Logistics Manager in Jabalpur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout TransIndia Logistics:\nTransIndia Logistics is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with TransIndia Logistics!",
